channel.title: ~<--i need a host--<~
channel.description:
I need someone to host my server.... my computer is just way to low on memory and my server freezes up my computer alot. :confused: The name of my server is WildyScape, personaly i think it is one of the best pk servers out there. It has loads of great commands and features that makes it that much more exciting.
If you decide to host my server i'll make you an owner, and you will get loads of advantages in the game!
I really need someone that will host my sever at least 10 hours a day... :( or maybe a bit less... if you are intrested email me at [email]wow5912@aol.com[/email] and at [email]fivenames6@msn.com[/email]
PLEASE if you are intrested please post that! :D[br][size=1]Posted on: April 11, 2007, 12:14:40 PM[/size][hr]Anyone there?.... I'll help you with editing your own server :)[br][size=1]Posted on: April 11, 2007, 03:18:55 PM[/size][hr]Just name your price, and we will talk about it.
